summary: Egypt Staff for Magic or Theme Modders Resource
descriptionHtml:
This is my third Work for an Egypt or Khajiit Themed Mod or Quest ,the Egypt Crook of the Pharaoh.
Again Modders can use it as their Stuff and do with it what they like/want ,No Permission needed.
Some will ask why i didnt mesh the Flail ,well cause i still hehe learning Meshing ,but i promise a Flail for the Set later :)
I hope you like it ,its a High poly Model of the Crook ,all is inside the File ,like dae.Blend and Maps AO + UV
Use it for anything you wanna create or do
Thx and Have Fun

Edit:

Now you got both Flail and Crook ,again no Permission needed ,use it as you like ,as Deco or as Sceptre for Magic or whatever :)
Enjoy
